<div
  id='pin-auth-modal'
  class='hidden fixed inset-0 bg-slate-900/40 backdrop-blur-sm flex items-center justify-center z-50'
>
  <div
    class='bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 w-full max-w-md p-6 relative mx-4'
  >
    <button
      onclick="toggleModal('pin-auth-modal')"
      class='absolute top-4 right-4 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 text-2xl font-semibold focus:outline-none'
    >&times;</button>
    <h3 class='text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-center'>Безопасный
      вход</h3>

    <form onsubmit='handleVerifyPinStepTwo(event)' class='space-y-4'>
      <div
        class='text-sm text-emerald-700 text-center bg-emerald-50 p-3 rounded-xl border border-emerald-200'
      >
        📨 Проверьте почту! Мы отправили вам 6-значный цифровой ПИН-код для
        подтверждения входа.
      </div>
      <div>
        <label
          class='block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase mb-2 text-center tracking-wider'
        >Введите полученный ПИН-код</label>
        <input
          type='text'
          id='login-pin-input'
          maxlength='6'
          placeholder='000000'
          required
          class='w-full text-center tracking-widest text-2xl font-bold px-3 py-2.5 border border-slate-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 bg-slate-50'
        />
      </div>

      <div class='text-center pt-1'>
        <button
          type='button'
          id='btn-resend-pin'
          onclick='handleResendPin()'
          disabled
          class='text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 cursor-not-allowed hover:text-indigo-600 transition focus:outline-none'
        >
          Отправить код повторно
        </button>
        <p id='resend-timer-text' class='text-[11px] text-slate-400 mt-1'>
          (можно через
          <span id='timer-seconds' class='font-bold text-slate-600'>60</span>
          сек)
        </p>
      </div>

      <button
        type='submit'
        class='w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-medium py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm transition shadow-sm font-semibold'
      >
        Подтвердить ПИН-код и войти
      </button>
      <button
        type='button'
        onclick="toggleModal('pin-auth-modal'); toggleModal('login-modal');"
        class='w-full text-xs text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600 text-center block'
      >
        ← Вернуться к вводу пароля
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>